Load Excel File Into Power Bi Desktop 6

Step 1 - Load Data Into Power Bi Desktop
  1. Click on the above red icon  to  download a zip file containing the Excel file, Colaberry logo, Police logo, and map legend
  2. Open Power Bi Desktop
  3. Select excel
  4. Select the downloaded excel file
  5. Click open
  6. Select the Fatal-Police-Shooting-Data sheet and

              Click on the Load button  to load the data into Power Bi Desktop
